Author: sammyonehouse
Title: [ANN][ICO] ALFATOKEN - A CROSS-CHAIN CRYPTOFINANCE MARKETPLACE
Body: Meet new advisor in our team!  David Drake is Founder and Chairman at LDJ Capital, a multi-family office which deals in worldwide funds accessing over several trillion in assets, and maintains over 50+ global directors and family office partners.  More recently, Drake is also seen as a leader in cryptocurrency. He saw the value of digital assets when everyone was avoiding it. It all started in 2011 when Drake collaborated on the JOBS Act to create new laws underlying all fundraising in the U.S. for all ICOs. He runs a $200M LDJ Cayman Fund focused on cryptocurrency, mining and ICO acquisitions. LDJ Capital Credit also offers middle market bridge financing to seed upcoming ICO’s. Previously he held a majority stake as a Managing Partner with Robert Hambrecht in an Alternative Energy Fund NewCommons Capital 2009-2010.  Drake was born in Sweden and is fluent in six languages. He holds an MBA in Finance and an MA in International Law and Economics from George Washington University in DC where he was awarded the Wallenberg Scholarship for academic merit.

Body: ALFA TOKEN Token and Smart Contract Manufacture Industry bambang (34) в cryptocurrency •  3 мecяцa нaзaд   Digital currency is a type of currency that is available only in digital form, not in physical form (such as banknotes and coins). It shows properties similar to physical currency, but allows instant transactions and unlimited transfer of ownership. Examples include virtual currency and crypto. Like traditional money, this currency can be used to purchase physical goods and services, but may also be limited to certain communities such as for use in online games or social networks. Digital currency is the money balance recorded electronically on a stored value card or other device. Another form of electronic money is network money, which enables value transfer on computer networks, especially the Internet. Electronic money is also a claim on private banks or other financial institutions such as bank deposits.

Author: Bonzai
Title: [ANN][ICO] ALFATOKEN - A CROSS-CHAIN CRYPTOFINANCE MARKETPLACE
Body: ★ WEBSITE ★ WHITEPAPER ★EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ★ TWITTER ★ TELEGRAM ★ REDDIT ★ FACEBOOK ★ YOUTUBE ★ VK  Pre-ICO Announcement  AlfaToken is a cryptofinance marketplace powered by smart contracts. AlfaToken is an automated, cryptographically secured, and cross-chain marketplace for the crypto economy that will allow to issue, borrow, lend, margin trade, and earn interest on the cryptocurrency. The marketplace consists from 5 services.   Our Partners     Services  ICO Smart Contracts — create without coding skills; AlfaLoans — get a loan by providing your project tokens; AlfaMargin — get a loan by providing a cryptocurrency; AlfaGages — get a loan by providing a tokenized real asset; AlfaDeposits — earn an interest on a cryptocurrency deposit.        MVP  The minimum viable product development of a service for building crowdsale smart contracts on Ethereum blockchain.        Core Team  Skilled and motivated team is a basis          Advisors          Roadmap  Here is our roadmap:          Dates  Pre ICO is starting on January 22, 2018 11 am GMT (UTC +0) and ending on April 22, 2018 11 am GMT (UTC +0) or when sold out whichever comes first.   Allocation of Tokens  Only 9 million ALFA tokens will ever be created. The ALFA tokens will be allocated as follows:      Price   The following discount on a wholesale basis for larger volume purchasers will be applied: • $5,000+ receives a 1.5% bonus; • $25,000+ receives a 10% bonus; • $100,000+ receives a 45% bonus.        Bonuses  During the ICO the following discount on a wholesale basis for larger volume purchasers will be applied:    $5,000+ receives a 1.5% bonus;  $25,000+ receives a 10% bonus;  $100,000+ receives a 45% bonus   Exchanges  We are planning to list ALFA tokens on a few exchanges after our Initial Coin Offering.    Moderator of this branch  sammyonehouse
